---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="TELOS | Problems Missions Goals and Life Direction" description="Personal framework for tracking purpose and direction in life">
  <main class="relative z-10 pt-28 pb-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl text-gradient mb-4">TELOS Framework</h1>
        <p class="font-body text-lg text-text-secondary">
          A structured approach to understanding problems, defining missions, setting goals, and measuring progress.
          Organized around three facets: <strong>GoodFields</strong> (Mind), <strong>FabLab</strong> (Hands), and <strong>StillPoint</strong> (Soul).
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Problems -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <span class="font-mono text-sm font-bold text-accent bg-accent/20 px-3 py-1 rounded">P</span>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl text-text-primary">Problems</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="font-body text-text-secondary mb-6">
          The most important issues I see that need solving.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-border-default p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <span class="font-mono text-sm font-bold text-accent shrink-0">P1</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-heading text-lg text-text-primary mb-2">People lack frameworks for finding and maintaining life purpose in an overstimulated world</h3>
                <p class="font-body text-sm text-text-secondary">
                  In a world of infinite distraction, people need structured approaches to connect daily action with deeper meaning.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-border-default p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <span class="font-mono text-sm font-bold text-accent shrink-0">P2</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-heading text-lg text-text-primary mb-2">Technical teams struggle to adopt AI safely without proper guardrails</h3>
                <p class="font-body text-sm text-text-secondary">
                  Organizations need frameworks to implement AI securely while maintaining data privacy and operational safety.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-border-default p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <span class="font-mono text-sm font-bold text-accent shrink-0">P3</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-heading text-lg text-text-primary mb-2">ADHD makes traditional productivity systems fail; different approaches needed</h3>
                <p class="font-body text-sm text-text-secondary">
                  Standard task management and workflow systems don't account for ADHD executive function challenges. We need systems that work with the brain, not against it.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-border-default p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <span class="font-mono text-sm font-bold text-accent shrink-0">P4</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-heading text-lg text-text-primary mb-2">Infrastructure knowledge is siloed; enterprise patterns should be accessible to everyone</h3>
                <p class="font-body text-sm text-text-secondary">
                  Enterprise-grade infrastructure patterns are locked behind corporate walls instead of shared for community benefit.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Missions -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <span class="font-mono text-sm font-bold text-brand bg-brand/20 px-3 py-1 rounded">M</span>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl text-text-primary">Missions</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="font-body text-text-secondary mb-6">
          My approaches to addressing these problems, aligned to three facets.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-border-default p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <span class="font-mono text-sm font-bold text-brand shrink-0">M1</span>
              <div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
                  <h3 class="font-heading text-lg text-text-primary">Build sustainable business that helps people thrive</h3>
                  <span class="font-mono text-xs text-accent bg-accent/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">Mind</span>
                </div>
                <p class="font-body text-sm text-text-secondary">
                  GoodFields — sovereignty, security, humane AI, and antifragile systems. Consulting and strategic work that generates resources for the broader mission.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-border-default p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <span class="font-mono text-sm font-bold text-brand shrink-0">M2</span>
              <div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
                  <h3 class="font-heading text-lg text-text-primary">Document enterprise-grade patterns at accessible scale</h3>
                  <span class="font-mono text-xs text-success bg-success/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">Hands</span>
                </div>
                <p class="font-body text-sm text-text-secondary">
                  FabLab — communal tools, local resilience, and creative infrastructure. Share production-grade patterns in reproducible, accessible formats.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-border-default p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <span class="font-mono text-sm font-bold text-brand shrink-0">M3</span>
              <div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
                  <h3 class="font-heading text-lg text-text-primary">Create conditions for presence and human flourishing through technology</h3>
                  <span class="font-mono text-xs text-warning bg-warning/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">Soul</span>
                </div>
                <p class="font-body text-sm text-text-secondary">
                  StillPoint — values, myth, and presence as technology. The foundation that guides everything. Technology should serve presence, not extract attention.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-6 bg-bg-secondary/50 rounded-xl border border-border-subtle p-4">
          <p class="font-body text-sm text-text-tertiary italic">
            The flow: GoodFields generates resources &rarr; FabLab demonstrates infrastructure &rarr; StillPoint documents the blueprint.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Goals -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <span class="font-mono text-sm font-bold text-success bg-success/20 px-3 py-1 rounded">G</span>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl text-text-primary">Goals</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="font-body text-text-secondary mb-6">
          Specific outcomes I'm working toward.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-border-default p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <span class="font-mono text-sm font-bold text-success shrink-0">G1</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-heading text-lg text-text-primary mb-2">Establish GoodFields as recognized security and AI consulting practice</h3>
                <p class="font-body text-sm text-text-secondary">
                  Build a reputation for pragmatic, security-first AI adoption consulting for technical teams.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-border-default p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <span class="font-mono text-sm font-bold text-success shrink-0">G2</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-heading text-lg text-text-primary mb-2">Build repeatable, documented infrastructure patterns anyone can learn from</h3>
                <p class="font-body text-sm text-text-secondary">
                  Create FabLab documentation that makes enterprise-grade patterns accessible and reproducible.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-border-default p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <span class="font-mono text-sm font-bold text-success shrink-0">G3</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-heading text-lg text-text-primary mb-2">Develop daily practices that compound — writing, movement, presence</h3>
                <p class="font-body text-sm text-text-secondary">
                  Build sustainable habits using ADHD-friendly systems: externalized memory, gentle accountability, and ship-and-iterate over rigid planning.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-border-default p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <span class="font-mono text-sm font-bold text-success shrink-0">G4</span>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-heading text-lg text-text-primary mb-2">Grow Greybeard AI Collective as Winnipeg's AI practitioner community</h3>
                <p class="font-body text-sm text-text-secondary">
                  Build a local community of AI practitioners focused on learning, sharing, and building together.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Footer -->
      <section class="border-t border-border-subtle pt-8">
        <p class="font-body text-sm text-text-tertiary italic">
          TELOS is my framework for purpose and direction. It's not about rigid planning — it's about knowing <em>why</em> so the <em>what</em> becomes clearer. The problems define the terrain. The missions chart the path. The goals emerge from aligned daily action.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
